{"title":"彷徨（外一首）","authors":["陈企霞"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"彷徨（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈企霞遗作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾向大海谈论小溪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海对我咆哮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒斥我：“看它不起。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾向小溪描述海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小溪对我讪笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘲弄我：“荒诞夸张。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一个要讳言自己来历；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一个不想知自己去处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我彷徨无地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自认是笨拙糊涂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你日日夜夜惊涛汹涌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿你年年月月细水长流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我岂肯以花言巧语而背弃真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁能知身后？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应绝喜或忧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶老日白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜面病更丑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无爱不能了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有恨皆勾销。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愧非止水心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸存容酒腹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大治获可卜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小我弃荣辱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时到目即瞑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"速朽乃至福！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（１９７７年．１１月．病中）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈企霞像  苗地画"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}